---
// Reusable ambient aurora for hero sections across the site. Continuous,
// CSS-only, covers the whole section, frozen under prefers-reduced-motion.
// Drop inside a `position: relative; overflow: hidden` hero wrapper.
---
<div class="aurora" aria-hidden="true">
  <span class="aurora-blob aurora-1"></span>
  <span class="aurora-blob aurora-2"></span>
  <span class="aurora-blob aurora-3"></span>
</div>
